snippet.textDisplay: I am an English convert to Islam bought up on British music and culture but i can honestly say I have never heard anything more beautiful. I met Shafqat Amanat Ali in London some years back and have never forgotten how humble and respectful he was. I lived for 12 years in Pakistan and these Coke studio pieces remind me of wonderful times spent there. This particular one is the best ever .
